Interface IVersioningService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VersioningService
    Deprecated. 
    - use CodeSystemRequests.prepareNewCodeSystemVersion() instead

    public interface IVersioningService
    Represents a terminology independent service responsible for collecting and creating versions for its concrete implementations.
